all_listings <- read_rds("All_Data/all_listings.rds")
all_listings <- all_listings %>%
  mutate(neighbourhood = as_factor(neighbourhood),
         room_type = as_factor(room_type)) %>%
  filter(availability_365 != 0)
price_by_neighbourhood <- all_listings %>%
  group_by(neighbourhood) %>%
  summarise(
    price = mean(price)
  )
price_by_type_neighbourhood <- all_listings %>%
  group_by(room_type, neighbourhood) %>%
  summarise(price = mean(price), n = n())


price_by_type_neighbourhood %>%
  filter(room_type == "Entire home/apt") %>%
  ggplot(aes(fct_reorder(neighbourhood, price), price)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() + 
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=6)) +
  labs(x = "Price per night",
       y = "Neighbborhood",
       title = "Price per neighborhood (Entire home/apt)")

price_by_type_neighbourhood %>%
  filter(room_type == "Private room") %>%
  ggplot(aes(fct_reorder(neighbourhood, price), price)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() + 
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=4)) +
    labs(x = "Price per night",
       y = "Neighbborhood",
       title = "Price per neighborhood (Private room)")

price_by_type_neighbourhood %>%
  filter(room_type == "Shared room") %>%
  ggplot(aes(fct_reorder(neighbourhood, price), price)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() + 
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=5)) +
  labs(x = "Price per night",
       y = "Neighbborhood",
       title = "Price per neighborhood (Shared room)")

price_by_type_neighbourhood %>%
  filter(room_type == "Hotel room") %>%
  ggplot(aes(fct_reorder(neighbourhood, price), price)) +
  geom_col() +
  coord_flip() + 
  theme(axis.text=element_text(size=10)) +
  labs(x = "Price per night",
       y = "Neighbborhood",
       title = "Price per neighborhood (Hotel room)")

### Visualizing Map Plot of Neighbourhood

price_quantiles <- price_by_type_neighbourhood$price %>%
  quantile(c(1/3, 2/3, 1)) %>%
  unname()


price_by_type_neighbourhood <- price_by_type_neighbourhood %>%
  mutate(
    price_category = ifelse(price <= price_quantiles[1], 'Low', 
                            ifelse(price > price_quantiles[1] & price <= price_quantiles[2], 'Medium', 'High'))
  )

price_cat <- all_listings %>%
  mutate(price_category = ifelse(price <= price_quantiles[1], 'Low', 
                            ifelse(price > price_quantiles[1] & price <= price_quantiles[2], 'Medium', 'High'))
  )

pal <- colorFactor(
  palette = "viridis",
  domain = price_cat$price_category)
leaflet(barrio) %>%
  addTiles() %>%
  addPolygons(weight = 1, color = "#444444", fill = FALSE) %>%
  addCircles(lng = ~price_cat$longitude, lat = ~price_cat$latitude, label = ~as.character(price_cat$price), color = ~pal(price_cat$price_category)) %>%
  addLegend("bottomleft", pal = pal, values = ~price_cat$price_category, title = "Price Category") 
calendar_prices <- read_rds("All_Data/calendar_prices.rds")
calendar_prices$price = as.numeric(gsub("\\$", "", calendar_prices$price))
## Warning: NAs introduced by coercion
#
calendar_prices %>%
  mutate(month_year = format(as.Date(date), "%Y-%m")) %>%
  group_by(month_year) %>%
  summarise(avg_price = mean(price,na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=month_year,y=avg_price, group = 1)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line(linetype='dotted') +
  labs(y = 'Price',
       x = 'Month',
       title = 'Price evolution on time')

DF2 <- all_listings %>%
   select(id, neighbourhood,longitude,latitude,room_type)

joined_data <- left_join(calendar_prices, DF2, by = c("listing_id" = "id"))
joined_data %>%
  filter(available == TRUE, !is.na(room_type)) %>%
  mutate(month_year = format(as.Date(date), "%Y-%m")) %>%
  group_by(month_year,room_type) %>%
  summarise(avg_price = mean(price, na.rm = TRUE)) %>%
  ggplot(aes(x=month_year,y=avg_price,group=room_type,color=room_type)) +
  geom_point() +
  geom_line(linetype='dotted') +
  labs(y = 'Price',
       x = 'Month',
       title = 'Price evolution on time')
